00:03:50.039 --> 00:03:50.800
I...

00:03:50.800 --> 00:03:52.080
I was wrong.

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:52.840
I...

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:54.560
I misjudged you.

00:03:54.599 --> 00:03:56.080
I failed to recognize true greatness.

00:03:56.159 --> 00:03:58.039
Young Hero, if you say we are a crooked sect,

00:03:58.039 --> 00:03:59.400
then we are a crooked sect.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:01.039
Please, do not kill me.

00:04:07.919 --> 00:04:09.120
Thank you.

00:04:11.439 --> 00:04:12.520
Hand over the antidote.

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:22.839
Thanks.

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:34.040
Is it fixed?

00:04:37.399 --> 00:04:38.199
It's fixed.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.040
Please take a look.

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:42.680
It's as good as new.

00:04:42.959 --> 00:04:44.079
Lock up

00:04:44.079 --> 00:04:46.480
this fat man,
along with those two traitors.

00:04:46.480 --> 00:04:47.079
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:04:48.730 --> 00:04:49.800
No need to trouble you two.

00:04:50.839 --> 00:04:51.680
Locked up is fine,

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:53.000
why are you making it personal?

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:53.800
Are you not fat?

00:04:53.800 --> 00:04:54.439
You...

00:04:58.079 --> 00:04:59.530
I'll do it myself.

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:04.480
Chun.

00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:07.360
Thank you for stepping in earlier.

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:09.319
You averted a catastrophe
for the martial world.

00:05:09.320 --> 00:05:11.080
True heroes are not judged
by their origins.

00:05:11.090 --> 00:05:12.959
I failed to see your true worth,

00:05:13.060 --> 00:05:14.220
and spoke without due respect.

00:05:14.230 --> 00:05:15.220
Please accept my apology.

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.959
Chun, I ask for your understanding.

00:05:16.959 --> 00:05:17.920
Not at all.

00:05:18.100 --> 00:05:18.839
You're too polite.

00:05:19.160 --> 00:05:19.720
Too polite.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:22.279
Thank you, Chun, for saving my life.

00:05:22.300 --> 00:05:23.079
I meant no offense.

00:05:23.279 --> 00:05:24.079
None taken.

00:05:25.519 --> 00:05:26.680
Esteemed elders, why don't we

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:27.959
sit down and discuss this?

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:36.040
In recent years, the Tianlong Cult
has grown increasingly powerful.

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:38.360
Yet our sects have remained divided.

00:05:38.530 --> 00:05:40.680
To prevent the Tianlong Cult
from growing too powerful

00:05:40.839 --> 00:05:42.519
and picking us off one by one,

00:05:42.759 --> 00:05:44.920
we have long discussed
with Sect Leader Tang

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:46.900
the matter of appointing
a new Alliance Leader.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.720
Before you arrived,

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:52.279
the four of us had already agreed

00:05:52.519 --> 00:05:55.079
to recommend Sect Leader Tang
for the position.

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:57.439
His martial skill surpasses all,

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:58.680
and his heart is broad and fair.

00:05:58.959 --> 00:06:01.639
He is capable of mediating disputes
among our sects.

00:06:01.959 --> 00:06:02.600
However,

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:03.839
his age has caught up with him,

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:05.360
and his health is failing.

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:08.879
This young man has inherited
Sect Leader Tang's teachings,

00:06:09.439 --> 00:06:11.279
and now bears the sect leader's seal.

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:12.560
I propose that

00:06:13.079 --> 00:06:13.959
we appoint

00:06:13.959 --> 00:06:15.199
this young man

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:16.560
as our new alliance leader.

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:18.000
What do you all think?

00:06:18.120 --> 00:06:18.720
Agreed.

00:06:22.759 --> 00:06:23.720
Me?

00:06:25.439 --> 00:06:26.680
Martial Arts Alliance Leader?

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:30.120
This...

00:06:30.319 --> 00:06:31.480
That doesn't seem appropriate.

00:06:33.319 --> 00:06:34.199
Esteemed elders,

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:36.560
please don't tease a junior like me.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.600
The position of alliance leader

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.360
carries great responsibility.

00:06:40.920 --> 00:06:41.959
I believe you all

00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:43.199
might want to

00:06:43.199 --> 00:06:44.360
give it more thought.

00:06:46.839 --> 00:06:47.680
Chun,

00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:49.319
take this advice from me.

00:06:49.639 --> 00:06:50.680
This is a good thing.

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:52.160
We shouldn't turn it down.

00:06:53.079 --> 00:06:53.720
Look,

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.040
your abilities,

00:06:55.519 --> 00:06:56.480
your martial skills,

00:06:56.879 --> 00:06:57.959
and even your

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.199
kind heart,

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:01.680
are clear for all to see.

00:07:01.879 --> 00:07:02.680
Young people

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:04.360
should step forward.

00:07:05.319 --> 00:07:06.000
On this matter,

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:06.879
we are all

00:07:06.879 --> 00:07:08.240
in unanimous agreement.

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:09.480
Come in.

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:21.319
This is the token
of the Alliance Leader,

00:07:21.319 --> 00:07:22.279
the White Jade Ring.

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:23.759
The previous leader

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:25.160
came from the Langya Sect

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:26.680
and was my late master.

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:28.480
He has since passed on.

00:07:28.680 --> 00:07:30.519
The position has remained vacant.

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:31.480
Today,

00:07:31.759 --> 00:07:33.839
after joint deliberation
by the major sect leaders,

00:07:34.279 --> 00:07:35.480
this ring is entrusted

00:07:36.399 --> 00:07:38.720
to the young hero Chun Ge.

00:07:39.839 --> 00:07:40.600
No, really,

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:42.120
everyone, I'm telling the truth...

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:42.759
Chun Ge,

00:07:43.480 --> 00:07:45.720
since Father entrusted you
with the sect seal,

00:07:46.600 --> 00:07:47.759
