00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:49.279
Besides, the alliance leadership

00:07:49.279 --> 00:07:51.360
has always rotated
among the great sects.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.279
Now it is our Cangqiong Sect's turn.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:55.160
This is the highest honor.

