00:09:19.310 --> 00:09:21.720
After all, you are now the Sect Leader
of the Cangqiong Sect,

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:23.390
and also
the Martial Arts Alliance Leader.

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:27.519
Is this really appropriate?

