Steady.

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:45.840
Master.

00:10:47.400 --> 00:10:49.540
Master. A lot of people have arrived
in the main hall.

00:10:49.559 --> 00:10:51.200
- Are they here to fight again?
- No.

00:10:51.210 --> 00:10:52.360
They are all here to see you.

00:10:52.590 --> 00:10:54.159
Have you seen the new alliance leader?

00:10:54.440 --> 00:10:55.399
No.

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:56.759
But I heard he's very young.

00:10:56.879 --> 00:10:57.440
