00:10:57.520 --> 00:10:58.799
The Alliance Leader has arrived.

00:10:59.330 --> 00:11:01.140
- Greetings, Alliance Leader.
- Greetings, Alliance Leader.

00:11:01.159 --> 00:11:02.600
Hey. What are you all doing?

00:11:02.600 --> 00:11:03.559
Please, get up.

00:11:04.279 --> 00:11:05.919
We have all come to congratulate

00:11:05.919 --> 00:11:08.320
Sect Leader Chun
on assuming the role of Alliance Leader.

00:11:08.330 --> 00:11:10.350
We have prepared a modest gift,
as a small token of respect.

00:11:10.360 --> 00:11:13.159
We also hope the Alliance Leader
will offer guidance and instruction,

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:14.350
for the benefit of the martial world.

00:11:14.360 --> 00:11:16.380
May the Alliance Leader
be blessed with great fortune.

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:17.759
- May your life and honor endure.
- May your life and honor endure.

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:19.000
All right.

00:11:20.240 --> 00:11:20.879
Everyone,

00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:22.240
you are far too kind.

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:25.950
We have heard that the Alliance Leader's
skills have advanced at remarkable speed.

00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:27.519
May we ask the Alliance Leader

00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:30.000
if there is a method
to understanding inner cultivation.

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:31.039
A method?

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:32.480
Yes.

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:34.840
My father often told me one thing.

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:37.510
Diligence makes up for lack of talent.

00:11:37.520 --> 00:11:39.000
True skill comes from persistence.

00:11:39.279 --> 00:11:40.440
What that means is...

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:41.200
We understand.

00:11:41.519 --> 00:11:42.799
The Alliance Leader means

00:11:42.799 --> 00:11:44.320
that effort matters most.

00:11:45.020 --> 00:11:46.920
Thank you for your guidance,
Alliance Leader.

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:47.720
Yes.

00:11:48.530 --> 00:11:49.559
You are very perceptive.

00:11:51.060 --> 00:11:53.039
Disciples of the Youyou Sect
greet the Alliance Leader.

00:11:53.039 --> 00:11:54.440
We humbly ask for your guidance.

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:56.480
How should one view cultivation?

00:11:57.080 --> 00:11:58.320
Cultivation itself...

00:11:58.799 --> 00:11:59.440
It

00:11:59.759 --> 00:12:00.679
must be driven by

00:12:02.679 --> 00:12:03.480
sincerity.

00:12:05.279 --> 00:12:06.000
I understand.

00:12:06.290 --> 00:12:06.720
Understand?

00:12:06.720 --> 00:12:07.690
The Alliance Leader means

00:12:07.700 --> 00:12:09.190
that as long as one cultivates
with true intent,

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:10.279
great progress will follow.

00:12:11.120 --> 00:12:12.470
Thank you for your clear guidance.

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:14.190
Disciples of Qinghe
greet the Alliance Leader.

00:12:14.200 --> 00:12:15.159
May I ask,

00:12:15.279 --> 00:12:17.960
how did you cultivate
such profound inner power?

00:12:27.159 --> 00:12:28.320
Besides

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:30.919
building one's own foundation,

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:34.759
one must also have

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:37.399
guidance from those more accomplished.

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:41.320
- Please lead us on the path.
- Please lead us on the path.

00:12:41.330 --> 00:12:43.750
May the Alliance Leader
bring blessings to the martial world.

00:12:45.530 --> 00:12:46.660
I do not deserve such praise.

00:12:46.679 --> 00:12:47.559
Thank you.

00:12:48.039 --> 00:12:48.720
Thank you.

00:12:52.279 --> 00:12:54.759
Seems being Master is no easy task.

00:12:56.519 --> 00:12:57.039
Min.

00:12:57.220 --> 00:12:57.960
You must be tired.

00:12:58.240 --> 00:13:00.799
I prepared a pot of herbal tea
to soothe your throat.

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:02.280
You really thought of everything.

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:05.360
Senior Brother is here too.

00:13:05.370 --> 00:13:06.559
I brought you some pastries.

00:13:06.559 --> 00:13:07.919
Perfect to have with the tea.

00:13:11.879 --> 00:13:13.039
What is this? It is so good.

00:13:13.279 --> 00:13:15.039
Your favorite osmanthus cake.

00:13:15.600 --> 00:13:16.559
You do not remember, Ge?

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:17.639
Yeah.

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.440
I just think this osmanthus cake

00:13:20.440 --> 00:13:21.440
is incredibly good.

00:13:21.759 --> 00:13:24.159
It tastes exactly
like the first one we ever had.

00:13:25.279 --> 00:13:26.120
But you know,

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:27.679
when we were kids,

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:30.080
we insisted there be no secrets at all.

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:32.559
No matter who it was,
even the tiniest little thing,

00:13:32.559 --> 00:13:33.919
had to be told to the other two.

00:13:34.559 --> 00:13:35.200
Right.

00:13:39.159 --> 00:13:40.480
Here. Have a couple more bites.

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:41.200
Wait.

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:43.480
Look.

00:13:43.799 --> 00:13:45.360
What do these three cakes look like?

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:48.279
I know. They look like
our three stones, right?

00:13:48.279 --> 00:13:48.879
Right.

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:50.320
You still keep them?

00:13:50.639 --> 00:13:51.159
Of course.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:13:52.440
So do I.

00:14:03.500 --> 00:14:05.990
Back then, no matter how hard you trained,
you just could not get it right,

00:14:06.159 --> 00:14:07.879
so Master punished you with confinement.

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:10.840
Min and I found a huge rock,

00:14:11.039 --> 00:14:13.559
trying to smash the lock
and get you out.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:14.399
Yeah.

00:14:14.600 --> 00:14:15.879
So this stone is a symbol

00:14:16.240 --> 00:14:18.039
of the friendship
between the three of us.

00:14:18.280 --> 00:14:19.960
No matter where I go,
I carry it with me,

00:14:20.360 --> 00:14:21.679
because whenever I see it,

00:14:22.039 --> 00:14:23.639
I think of you two.

00:14:27.080 --> 00:14:27.879
Chun,

00:14:28.500 --> 00:14:31.120
I never imagined the little junior brother
who once needed rescuing

00:14:31.860 --> 00:14:33.679
would become
the Martial Arts Alliance Leader.

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:36.600
What I could not achieve,

00:14:37.679 --> 00:14:38.559
you have done.

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:42.879
Ge,

00:14:43.759 --> 00:14:44.639
I truly believe

00:14:45.159 --> 00:14:46.720
with your current mastery,

00:14:47.190 --> 00:14:49.000
you will be able
to lead the Cangqiong Sect,

00:14:49.180 --> 00:14:50.600
along with the four great sects,

00:14:51.000 --> 00:14:52.200
to defeat the Tianlong Cult,

00:14:52.840 --> 00:14:55.440
and bring peace back to the people
and to the martial world.

00:15:06.200 --> 00:15:06.919
Su.

00:15:08.240 --> 00:15:09.000
Min.

00:15:11.279 --> 00:15:12.080
I think

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:14.600
there is something

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:15.799
I have to tell you.

00:15:18.279 --> 00:15:19.720
The truth is, my inner power

00:15:20.440 --> 00:15:22.159
it... It actually comes from that sword...

00:15:22.159 --> 00:15:22.879
Master!

00:15:23.039 --> 00:15:25.200
Su! Something terrible has happened!
The Langya Sect

00:15:25.200 --> 00:15:26.720
has been ambushed by the Tianlong Cult!

00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:27.480
What?

00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:33.679
Save them.

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:35.919
What happened?

00:15:36.120 --> 00:15:36.790
Alliance Leader.

00:15:37.360 --> 00:15:38.000
Alliance Leader.

