No need for formalities.

00:15:39.559 --> 00:15:40.080
Tell me

00:15:40.399 --> 00:15:41.240
exactly what happened.

00:15:41.250 --> 00:15:43.790
The Tianlong Cult launched
a surprise attack on the Langya Sect,

00:15:43.800 --> 00:15:45.000
abducted Bao Wuji,

00:15:45.399 --> 00:15:47.759
and slaughtered many of their disciples.

00:15:48.360 --> 00:15:49.960
Such brutality.

00:15:49.960 --> 00:15:50.960
They are clearly trying

00:15:50.960 --> 00:15:53.480
to wipe out every sect, one by one.

00:15:54.240 --> 00:15:55.200
At this point,

00:15:55.519 --> 00:15:56.879
we must strike first.

00:15:57.080 --> 00:15:57.840
Otherwise,

00:15:57.960 --> 00:15:59.919
more tragedies will follow.

00:16:00.320 --> 00:16:01.919
You must uphold justice for us,

00:16:01.919 --> 00:16:02.759
Alliance Leader.

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:14.639
You chose me as the Alliance Leader.

00:16:16.559 --> 00:16:18.200
To me, all of this

00:16:20.799 --> 00:16:22.200
feels like a dream.

00:16:23.039 --> 00:16:24.039
The person I once was

00:16:24.039 --> 00:16:26.320
would have believed
I was unworthy of this title.

00:16:28.879 --> 00:16:30.240
But at this moment,

00:16:33.480 --> 00:16:35.000
I will no longer think that way.

00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:41.759
I now call upon all sect leaders

00:16:43.159 --> 00:16:44.440
and disciples of every path

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:46.559
to stand with me

00:16:47.050 --> 00:16:48.799
and march
on the Tianlong Cult stronghold.

00:16:50.080 --> 00:16:52.159
Together, we will reclaim

00:16:52.840 --> 00:16:54.120
the peace that should be ours.

00:17:19.340 --> 00:17:22.900
(Tianlong Cult)

00:17:44.210 --> 00:17:44.920
Alliance Leader.

00:17:45.410 --> 00:17:46.240
Something feels off.

00:17:46.559 --> 00:17:48.039
Not a single person tried to stop us.

00:17:48.359 --> 00:17:49.519
It went a little too smoothly.

00:17:50.599 --> 00:17:51.960
(We're already here.)

00:17:52.160 --> 00:17:53.519
(No turning back now.)

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:55.599
Everyone inside, listen up.

00:17:56.079 --> 00:17:57.599
I am the Martial Arts Alliance Leader,

00:17:57.860 --> 00:17:59.599
Chun Ge, Sect Leader
of the Cangqiong Sect.

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:01.200
Have your Cult Master

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:02.559
Long Zhentian come out and face me.

00:18:09.559 --> 00:18:10.279
Alliance Leader.

00:18:10.920 --> 00:18:12.079
Please be careful later.

00:18:32.220 --> 00:18:36.500
(Long Zhentian, Tianlong Cult Master.
Combat Power)

00:18:38.079 --> 00:18:39.319
Long Zhentian.

00:18:40.519 --> 00:18:41.839
You abducted Bao Wuji,

00:18:42.599 --> 00:18:44.319
slaughtered the Langya Sect,

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:47.119
acted with utter arrogance,
committed countless atrocities,

00:18:47.359 --> 00:18:48.400
and shattered the peace.

00:18:49.039 --> 00:18:50.200
The martial world

00:18:50.920 --> 00:18:52.599
has long reached its limit with you.

00:18:53.359 --> 00:18:55.599
Today, the five great sects stand united

00:18:55.759 --> 00:18:57.119
to demand justice.

00:18:58.279 --> 00:18:59.079
Today,

00:19:00.240 --> 00:19:02.920
I will make you answer
for every drop of blood.

00:19:03.240 --> 00:19:04.480
Blood for blood.

00:19:04.490 --> 00:19:05.950
- Blood for blood.
- Blood for blood.

00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:07.500
- Blood for blood.
- Blood for blood.

00:19:08.359 --> 00:19:09.799
Who do you think you are?

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:11.279
Such bold words.

00:19:11.599 --> 00:19:12.640
(That voice.)

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:14.960
(It sounds strangely familiar.)

00:19:15.160 --> 00:19:17.920
You old rascal. How dare you speak
to the Alliance Leader like that.

00:19:18.079 --> 00:19:19.680
Martial Arts Alliance Leader?

00:19:20.319 --> 00:19:22.680
You fringe sects and crooked paths

00:19:22.680 --> 00:19:24.799
picked a green kid like him

00:19:24.799 --> 00:19:26.400
and call him Alliance Leader?

00:19:26.559 --> 00:19:27.480
On what grounds?

00:19:27.720 --> 00:19:29.200
Because we trust him.

00:19:29.200 --> 00:19:29.920
Exactly.

00:19:30.079 --> 00:19:32.240
His inner power surpasses all of ours.

00:19:32.319 --> 00:19:33.680
(Enough.)

00:19:33.680 --> 00:19:35.200
(Don't hype me up like that.)

00:19:37.559 --> 00:19:38.319
Inner power?

00:19:38.799 --> 00:19:40.119
That makes it even more laughable.

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:42.880
An ordinary disciple
of the Cangqiong Sect

00:19:42.880 --> 00:19:44.440
suddenly surges in power,

00:19:45.079 --> 00:19:49.000
and within days subdues sect leaders
who trained for decades.

00:19:49.559 --> 00:19:50.720
Isn't that absurd?

00:19:51.240 --> 00:19:53.440
Did you ever ask him

00:19:53.599 --> 00:19:55.240
where that power came from?

00:20:01.880 --> 00:20:02.640
Inner power

00:20:03.279 --> 00:20:04.200
needs no pedigree.

00:20:04.599 --> 00:20:05.559
Only strength matters.

00:20:06.240 --> 00:20:07.440
Enough talk.

00:20:07.920 --> 00:20:08.720
Let us

00:20:08.960 --> 00:20:09.960
take him down together.

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:15.680
That's right.

00:20:16.440 --> 00:20:18.240
Since everyone believes in me,

00:20:19.079 --> 00:20:20.039
then it is my duty

00:20:21.279 --> 00:20:23.640
to bring that peace
back to the martial world.

00:20:48.559 --> 00:20:49.559
Kid,

00:20:49.880 --> 00:20:51.400
your cultivation is indeed impressive.

00:20:51.720 --> 00:20:53.759
If you earned it
through your own training,

00:20:54.079 --> 00:20:56.079
you might actually deserve respect.

00:20:56.720 --> 00:20:57.680
Unfortunately...

00:20:58.559 --> 00:20:59.359
What do you mean?

00:20:59.599 --> 00:21:00.839
I mean

00:21:01.400 --> 00:21:02.839
you're a fraud.

00:21:03.359 --> 00:21:04.000
A fraud?

00:21:08.279 --> 00:21:09.640
I haven't deceived anyone.

00:21:10.720 --> 00:21:11.799
If you've got the guts,

00:21:12.039 --> 00:21:13.240
then come at me again.

00:21:14.519 --> 00:21:15.759
You didn't lie?

00:21:16.839 --> 00:21:18.680
Then do you recognize me?

00:21:31.799 --> 00:21:33.880
I will give you one last chance.

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:37.119
Tell these allies of the martial world

00:21:37.720 --> 00:21:38.799
who trust you

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:40.799
where your inner power truly came from.

00:21:52.160 --> 00:21:53.839
I do not care how it was obtained.

00:21:58.319 --> 00:22:00.039
As long as that power is within me,

00:22:00.720 --> 00:22:02.119
it belongs to me.

00:22:26.759 --> 00:22:27.519
Chun,

00:22:27.519 --> 00:22:28.279
how could this be?

00:22:28.640 --> 00:22:29.480
This cannot be true.

00:22:29.720 --> 00:22:31.079
Why would it be impossible?

00:22:31.480 --> 00:22:33.279
A complete scoundrel like him

00:22:33.640 --> 00:22:36.799
managed, in just a few days,

00:22:36.799 --> 00:22:38.680
to deceive the entire martial world

00:22:38.680 --> 00:22:39.880
and win your blind devotion.

00:22:40.839 --> 00:22:42.440
It is laughable.

00:22:50.279 --> 00:22:52.200
He is draining
the Alliance Leader's inner power.

00:22:52.319 --> 00:22:53.279
That makes no sense.

00:22:58.200 --> 00:22:59.759
Now you are nothing but a cripple.

00:23:00.319 --> 00:23:01.039
Tell them

00:23:01.759 --> 00:23:04.119
why I am able
to take this power from you.

00:23:21.960 --> 00:23:23.119
Because...

00:23:25.759 --> 00:23:27.119
Because my inner power

00:23:30.759 --> 00:23:31.839
was given to me by him.

00:23:32.630 --> 00:23:34.079
How could it have been given by him?

00:23:34.440 --> 00:23:35.480
How could this happen?

00:23:36.200 --> 00:23:37.599
How could such a thing exist?

00:23:41.720 --> 00:23:42.759
Once, I believed

00:23:44.680 --> 00:23:46.720
that he was
the Sword Immortal Bai Qiongyu.

00:23:49.039 --> 00:23:50.400
So I trusted him without doubt.

00:23:54.640 --> 00:23:56.240
My inner power was given to me by him.

00:23:59.519 --> 00:24:00.720
I was nothing more than

00:24:01.799 --> 00:24:03.839
an ordinary disciple
of the Cangqiong Sect.

00:24:05.640 --> 00:24:07.480
No one ever truly noticed me.

00:24:09.400 --> 00:24:11.119
The envy you now feel,

00:24:12.119 --> 00:24:13.279
the praise you now speak,

00:24:16.279 --> 00:24:18.119
were things
I never even dared to imagine.

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:22.960
So,

00:24:26.119 --> 00:24:28.119
after I gained this power,

00:24:29.519 --> 00:24:31.279
I cherished it all the more

00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:33.799
and did not want to reveal the truth.

00:24:35.559 --> 00:24:36.480
I am sorry.

00:24:39.519 --> 00:24:40.440
I am sorry.

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:47.160
You all heard that, didn't you?

00:24:48.640 --> 00:24:51.440
The so-called supreme
Alliance Leader you chose

00:24:51.880 --> 00:24:54.440
turned out to be nothing but a fraud.

00:24:55.960 --> 00:24:57.559
A martial world like this

00:24:58.119 --> 00:24:59.960
is it not a complete joke?

00:25:03.900 --> 00:25:05.640
I knew there was
something wrong with you.

00:25:05.640 --> 00:25:07.880
Did not expect you to sink this low.

00:25:08.400 --> 00:25:10.039
Linglong Sect disciples,
heed my command.

00:25:10.599 --> 00:25:11.440
We withdraw.

00:25:11.440 --> 00:25:12.039
Wait.

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:13.759
He may have deceived us,

00:25:13.759 --> 00:25:15.640
but the Langya Sect
still deserves justice.

00:25:15.640 --> 00:25:16.880
How can you just leave?

00:25:17.400 --> 00:25:18.200
If we stay,

00:25:18.480 --> 00:25:21.240
are we to let a liar decide
the fate of the martial world?

00:25:21.720 --> 00:25:22.440
We are leaving.

00:25:22.759 --> 00:25:23.160
Move.

00:25:23.680 --> 00:25:24.200
Go.

00:25:29.720 --> 00:25:31.559
The Qinghe Sect and the Cangqiong Sect

00:25:31.559 --> 00:25:33.279
have always stood or fallen together.

00:25:33.599 --> 00:25:34.559
But today,

00:25:35.119 --> 00:25:36.880
you have truly disappointed us.

00:25:37.920 --> 00:25:38.590
As things stand,

00:25:39.079 --> 00:25:40.400
with just us here,

00:25:40.400 --> 00:25:42.119
we cannot contend
with the Tianlong Cult.

00:25:42.880 --> 00:25:44.039
We should withdraw for now

00:25:44.039 --> 00:25:45.279
and plan our next move.

00:25:45.519 --> 00:25:46.279
You may leave.

00:25:48.119 --> 00:25:48.960
We are staying.

00:25:51.200 --> 00:25:52.000
Retreat.

00:25:56.519 --> 00:25:59.960
You people talk about the martial world
day in and day out.

00:26:00.799 --> 00:26:01.519
Is this

00:26:02.599 --> 00:26:05.039
what you call the martial world?

00:26:07.599 --> 00:26:09.680
They can all walk away,

00:26:10.759 --> 00:26:12.119
but I cannot.

00:26:13.680 --> 00:26:16.240
The Langya Sect exists in name only now.

00:26:16.480 --> 00:26:18.720
Staying behind serves no purpose.

00:26:19.559 --> 00:26:20.440
Today,

00:26:21.440 --> 00:26:23.920
I will seek justice

00:26:25.599 --> 00:26:27.599
for the brothers who died.

00:26:38.720 --> 00:26:40.279
Sect Leader Lu!

00:26:41.319 --> 00:26:42.440
You saw it yourself.

00:26:43.359 --> 00:26:45.119
He did not have to die.

00:26:45.680 --> 00:26:47.680
But he trusted you.

00:26:48.000 --> 00:26:49.759
You used the inner power I gave you

00:26:49.920 --> 00:26:52.720
to stir the sects
into opposing the Tianlong Cult.

00:26:53.039 --> 00:26:53.759
Today,

00:26:54.319 --> 00:26:55.599
I cannot let you live.

00:26:56.200 --> 00:26:57.319
Cangqiong Sect, form up.

00:27:00.160 --> 00:27:01.000
Long Zhentian.

00:27:01.400 --> 00:27:03.160
Chun Ge may be our acting sect leader,

00:27:03.720 --> 00:27:05.160
but he is also our friend.

00:27:06.160 --> 00:27:08.039
If you dare lay
a hand on him again today,

00:27:08.559 --> 00:27:09.759
the Cangqiong Sect

00:27:09.759 --> 00:27:11.240
will fight you to the death.

00:27:12.359 --> 00:27:14.400
Then you will all die.

00:27:17.759 --> 00:27:18.559
Wait.

00:27:23.559 --> 00:27:25.799
Your Tianlong Cult
seeks nothing but domination.

00:27:26.400 --> 00:27:26.960
And you

00:27:27.500 --> 00:27:29.640
style yourself the supreme ruler
of the martial world.

00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:32.160
Yet countless sects
refuse to submit to you,

00:27:33.240 --> 00:27:35.039
because you rely solely on brute force,

00:27:35.880 --> 00:27:37.920
wiping out other sects without mercy.

00:27:38.359 --> 00:27:39.800
There is no honor in such victories.

00:27:40.079 --> 00:27:40.720
Today,

00:27:41.480 --> 00:27:42.480
the Cangqiong Sect

00:27:43.200 --> 00:27:44.839
formally challenges the Tianlong Cult.

00:27:45.250 --> 00:27:47.460
On another day,
we settle this in a fight to the death.

00:27:47.839 --> 00:27:49.119
The loser submits to any fate,

00:27:49.290 --> 00:27:50.599
willingly and without complaint.

00:27:51.039 --> 00:27:52.200
If you win,

00:27:52.880 --> 00:27:54.759
the other sects
will acknowledge your strength.

00:27:56.799 --> 00:27:59.960
Today, the entire martial world
gathered at my Tianlong Cult's gates,

00:28:00.359 --> 00:28:02.440
yet you scattered without a fight,
like loose sand.

00:28:02.880 --> 00:28:04.599
How is that an unearned victory?

00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:07.680
And why would I care for
the regard of ants like you?

00:28:08.799 --> 00:28:09.759
This cripple,

00:28:09.920 --> 00:28:11.000
you may take him away.

00:28:11.640 --> 00:28:12.640
In three days,

00:28:12.880 --> 00:28:15.440
the Tianlong Cult
will bathe the Cangqiong Sect in blood.

00:28:18.359 --> 00:28:19.160
We leave.

00:28:22.440 --> 00:28:23.279
Chun.

00:28:36.599 --> 00:28:37.279
Cult Master,

00:28:37.599 --> 00:28:39.240
why give them three days?

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:40.319
Fear

00:28:41.519 --> 00:28:44.079
is the most insidious poison
in this world.

00:28:44.880 --> 00:28:46.559
It erodes resolve

00:28:46.559 --> 00:28:47.839
and corrodes one's nature.

00:28:48.680 --> 00:28:49.839
These three days,

00:28:50.759 --> 00:28:54.279
I will let the entire martial world
taste what it means to wait for death.

00:28:54.930 --> 00:28:55.990
Wise as ever, Cult Master.

00:28:56.440 --> 00:28:57.480
But that inner power

00:28:57.900 --> 00:28:59.119
was it truly passed on by you?

00:29:06.880 --> 00:29:08.680
That was merely a tactic
to break his will.

00:29:09.599 --> 00:29:11.039
If the Sword Immortal's power

00:29:11.039 --> 00:29:13.480
were unleashed without distraction,

00:29:13.880 --> 00:29:14.599
this battle

00:29:14.599 --> 00:29:15.720
might not end in our favor.

00:29:18.440 --> 00:29:19.200
Back.

00:29:19.380 --> 00:29:28.460
(Tianlong Cult)

00:29:33.640 --> 00:29:34.200
Everyone,

00:29:35.119 --> 00:29:36.359
I have explained the situation.

00:29:36.800 --> 00:29:38.319
This concerns the survival of our sect

00:29:38.319 --> 00:29:39.559
and your very lives.

00:29:39.920 --> 00:29:41.519
I have no right to decide for you.

00:29:42.119 --> 00:29:43.279
If anyone wishes to leave,

00:29:43.640 --> 00:29:44.880
I will not stop you.

00:29:46.039 --> 00:29:47.119
But if you choose to stay,

00:29:47.839 --> 00:29:49.400
then stand with me, Su Beilu,

00:29:49.780 --> 00:29:51.440
and defend the Cangqiong Sect
to the end.

00:29:53.519 --> 00:29:55.160
Staying here means death.

00:30:03.880 --> 00:30:04.880
I am sorry, Beilu.

00:30:05.160 --> 00:30:05.759
I...

00:30:06.119 --> 00:30:07.319
I am my family's only son.

00:30:07.600 --> 00:30:08.780
I have to leave the mountain.

00:30:10.800 --> 00:30:12.210
Senior Brother Zhang is going first.

00:30:12.279 --> 00:30:13.119
We should go too.

00:30:15.000 --> 00:30:16.580
I still have an elderly mother at home.

00:30:17.200 --> 00:30:17.880
I am sorry.

00:30:20.079 --> 00:30:22.650
I will never forget the kindness shown
by the Sect Leader and you.

00:30:22.920 --> 00:30:23.599
Take care.

00:30:44.119 --> 00:30:44.839
Beilu...

00:30:44.839 --> 00:30:46.079
No need to say more.

00:30:48.559 --> 00:30:49.640
These past days,

00:30:50.240 --> 00:30:51.240
being with all of you,

00:30:52.920 --> 00:30:54.160
I was truly happy.

00:30:55.160 --> 00:30:56.119
And it was worth it.

00:30:56.920 --> 00:30:57.599
Wanting to leave

00:30:58.039 --> 00:30:59.359
is only natural.

00:31:00.240 --> 00:31:02.440
I do not want you deciding
in the heat of the moment.

00:31:03.519 --> 00:31:04.599
Go back first.

00:31:05.720 --> 00:31:06.759
Those who wish to stay,

00:31:07.400 --> 00:31:08.359
in three days' time,

00:31:09.359 --> 00:31:10.400
gather in the courtyard.

00:31:37.880 --> 00:31:38.680
Beilu,

00:31:39.519 --> 00:31:40.599
if others choose to leave,

00:31:41.039 --> 00:31:41.960
I will not stop them.

00:31:43.599 --> 00:31:44.559
But I hope

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.039
you will stay.

00:31:49.000 --> 00:31:49.680
You,

00:31:50.240 --> 00:31:50.920
me,

00:31:51.680 --> 00:31:52.440
Min.

00:31:53.599 --> 00:31:55.640
We were the first
to enter Master's tutelage.

00:31:56.480 --> 00:31:57.599
The Cangqiong Sect

00:31:58.559 --> 00:31:59.680
is our home.

00:32:01.119 --> 00:32:02.680
I hope you can stay with us

00:32:03.400 --> 00:32:04.599
and hold the mountain gate.

00:32:07.160 --> 00:32:08.319
As I am now,

00:32:11.000 --> 00:32:12.359
my inner power is gone.

00:32:13.279 --> 00:32:15.279
To be blunt, I am useless.

00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:17.759
If a useless man stays,

00:32:20.039 --> 00:32:21.160
what difference does it make?

00:32:21.279 --> 00:32:22.519
Who says you are useless?

00:32:23.079 --> 00:32:24.119
Master once said,

00:32:25.160 --> 00:32:26.440
when everyone stands together,

00:32:26.920 --> 00:32:28.480
even metal can be cut.

00:32:31.039 --> 00:32:32.240
I believe

00:32:33.279 --> 00:32:34.559
that if we join forces,

00:32:36.279 --> 00:32:38.119
we can defeat Long Zhentian.

00:32:39.119 --> 00:32:40.480
And even if we fail,

00:32:41.119 --> 00:32:42.839
at least we will have given everything.

00:32:52.400 --> 00:32:53.519
I am not like you.

00:32:54.880 --> 00:32:55.839
Ever since we were kids,

00:32:56.240 --> 00:32:57.240
you were tall and strong.

00:32:58.759 --> 00:32:59.920
Good at sports,

00:33:02.039 --> 00:33:03.400
all the boys in class

00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:06.519
looked up to you.

00:33:07.759 --> 00:33:09.279
They all wanted to be you.

00:33:10.480 --> 00:33:11.640
But me?

00:33:15.119 --> 00:33:16.599
I was bullied growing up.

